MyVoice 2020 Annual Report

About

Youth are experts of their own experiences and the MyVoice team believes we need to listen to the experts! MyVoice connects with young people through weekly text message polls. Real-time data collection and rapid expert analysis of responses allow us to quickly share youth voices with those seeking to understand what youth think, experience, and need.
